Package: homa2calc
Title: HOMA2 Insulin Resistance and Beta-Cell Function Calculator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Your", "Name", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Computes HOMA2 %B (beta-cell function), HOMA2 %S (insulin
    sensitivity), and HOMA2-IR using bilinear interpolation over reference
    tables derived from the HOMA2 Calculator v2.2.4 validation dataset
    (Diabetes Trials Unit, University of Oxford). Supports three input modes:
    non-specific insulin, specific (proinsulin-free) insulin, and C-peptide.
    Works on any platform including Linux HPC environments.
